		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" /><div class="quotetitle">80sFREAK wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">That's pretty clear - use as much resources as PPU can provide. One question - VRAM chip static only or i can use pseudo static RAM as well?</div>
<br />Pseudo static RAM use CS toggle for prefetch. So, it can't be used here. Use SRAM, it's cheap and widely distributed.

		

